Insider Activity


Individual




Lawrence D. McRae



Mr. Lawrence D. McRae is Vice Chairman & Corporate Development Officer at Corning, Inc. He is on the Board of Directors at Dow Corning Corp., Samsung Corning Co. Ltd., Samsung Corning Precision Materials Co., Ltd., Samsung Corning Advanced Glass LLC, and Corning, Inc. Foundation.
Mr. McRae was previously employed as President by Revere Ware Corp., Vice President by Corning Consumer Products Co., and Senior Accountant by PricewaterhouseCoopers LLP.
He received his undergraduate degree from Morgan State University and a graduate degree from Harvard University.



