To the Trade


In order for you and your clients to get to know the Lawrence McRae brand, it is important for us to give you the tools you need. With that, we invite you to be part of our VIP Trade Package. In this package you will receive a binder complete with images of all the pieces in the Lawrence McRae Ceramics line, as well as a chip box with all the colors chosen for this years collection. When you join the VIP Trade Package, you will also receive our 20% designer discount.
If you are an interior designer or a store and would like to work together, but don’t need the binder and chips - that’s great too! Please email: info@lawrencemcrae.com











